array.note: x[i][j] is 1 (resp., 2), if a black (resp., white) queen is in the cell at row i and column j. It is 0 otherwise.

var.note: nb is the number of black queens
nw is the number of white queens

group.note: no two opponent queens can attack each other

count.note: counting the number of black queens
counting the number of white queens

maximize.note: maximizing the number of black queens (and consequently, the size of the armies)
